%spark

import scala.util.Try
import scala.xml._

case class Hotel(name : String, locality : String, country : String, avgRating: Double)

//val path = "/data/tripadvisor/json/99292.json"
val path = "/data/tripadvisor/json/*.json"
val hotelDF = sqlContext.read.json(path)
val hotels = hotelDF.select("Reviews.Ratings.Overall", "HotelInfo.Name", "HotelInfo.Address").map(hotel => Try({
    val xml = XML.loadString(hotel.getString(2))
    val locality = (xml \\ "span").filter(_.attribute("property").exists(_.text == "v:locality")).text
    var country = (xml \\ "span").filter(_.attribute("property").exists(_.text == "v:country-name")).text
    country = if (country == "") "USA" else country
    
    val overall: Seq[String] = hotel.getSeq(0)
    val ratings = overall.map(s => Try(s.toDouble)).filter(_.isSuccess).map(_.get)
    val avg = (0.0 /: ratings){_ + _} / ratings.length
    
    Hotel(hotel.getString(1), locality, country, avg)
}))
.filter(_.isSuccess).map(_.get)



hotels.toDF.registerTempTable("hotels")
